The paper deals with the problem of encoding and decoding data using prefix codes, which is a fundamental problem in computer science. The paper proposes a new data structure that allows for fast and compact prefix codes. This problem is closely related to data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), coding theory (cs.CC), signal processing (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
